{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/post/hotaru-itb-ciayo-comics-datang-lagi-ke-bandung/","result":{"data":{"wordpressPost":{"title":"HOTARU ITB: CIAYO Comics Datang Lagi ke Bandung!","content":"<p>Halo bro sis Bandung! Udah pada mampir ke <a href=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/pakoban-x-ciayo-comics/\">event komik di Bandung</a> minggu kemarin? Tim CIAYO Comics udah ketemu banyak banget penggemar komik di ciayo.com. Namun, kami juga denger kalau banyak bro sis yang nggak bisa datang ke <em>event</em> itu. Wah, kasihan ya&#8230;</p>\n<p><em>Eits, </em>jangan sedih dulu! Karena minggu ini CIAYO Comics bakal hadir lagi ke Bandung <em>lho</em>!</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_3515\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3515\" data-attachment-id=\"3515\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/hotaru-itb-ciayo-comics-datang-lagi-ke-bandung/attachment/body8-13/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/body8-5.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Poster HOTARU 6 (Facebook.com)\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Poster HOTARU 6 (Facebook.com)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/body8-5-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/body8-5.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-3515\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/body8-5.jpg\" alt=\"Poster HOTARU 6 (Facebook.com)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/body8-5.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/body8-5-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-3515\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Poster HOTARU 6 (Facebook.com)</p></div></p>\n<p>Yup! CIAYO Comics bakal hadir ke acara <strong>HOTARU 6</strong>. Apa sih HOTARU 6? Jadi HOTARU (Heiwa no Tabi ga Hajimaru 6) adalah festival Jepang di Bandung yang membawa diri kamu masuk ke dalam Cerita &amp; Roleplay. Event ini diselenggarakan oleh Unit Kebudayaan Jepang (UKJ) dari universitas Institut Teknologi Bandung (ITB). HOTARU adalah acara tahunan yang banyak diminati oleh penggemar kebudayaan Jepang seperti Anime, Cosplay, Kuliner Jepang, dan lain-lainnya.</p>\n<p>Di HOTARU 6, bro sis juga bisa nemuin berbagai macam acara seperti:</p>\n<p><strong>Roleplay</strong></p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_3506\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3506\" data-attachment-id=\"3506\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/hotaru-itb-ciayo-comics-datang-lagi-ke-bandung/attachment/body5-21/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/body5-8.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Aphin (Facebook.com)\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Aphin (Facebook.com)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/body5-8-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/body5-8.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-3506\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/body5-8.jpg\" alt=\"Aphin (Facebook.com)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/body5-8.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/body5-8-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-3506\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Aphin (Facebook.com)</p></div></p>\n<p>APHIN adalah sosok cosplayer yang terkenal dengan <em>skill makeup</em> karakter. Berawal dari kepiawaiannya mengubah gender (cosplay/crossplay) dan pilihan range karakter, mulai dari serial Jepang hingga Western. Kepiawaiannya itu membuatnya memiliki fanbase yang solid di <em>social media</em> dari berbagai belahan dunia.</p>\n<p><strong>Band Performance</strong></p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_3500\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3500\" data-attachment-id=\"3500\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/hotaru-itb-ciayo-comics-datang-lagi-ke-bandung/attachment/body4-21/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/body4-9.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Yuuki Tachi (Facebook.com)\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Yuuki Tachi (Facebook.com)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/body4-9-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/body4-9.jpg\" class=\"wp-image-3500 size-full\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/body4-9.jpg\" alt=\"Yuukitachi (Facebook.com)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/body4-9.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/body4-9-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-3500\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Yuukitachi (Facebook.com)</p></div></p>\n<p>Yuukitachi merupakan grup band asal Indonesia yang khusus membawakan cover-cover lagu berbau Jepang dan khususnya garnidelia. Beranggotakan 5 orang, Nisa dan Chy sebagai vokalis, Andro sebagai gitaris, Regy sebagai bassis, dan Junno sebagai drummer.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_3494\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3494\" data-attachment-id=\"3494\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/hotaru-itb-ciayo-comics-datang-lagi-ke-bandung/attachment/body1-23/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/body1-11.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Divisi Musik UKJ ITB\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Divisi Musik UKJ ITB (Facebook.com)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/body1-11-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/body1-11.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-3494\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/body1-11.jpg\" alt=\"Divisi Musik UKJ ITB (Facebook.com)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/body1-11.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/body1-11-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-3494\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Divisi Musik UKJ ITB (Facebook.com)</p></div></p>\n<p>Divisi musik UKJ adalah salah satu divisi di UKJ yang berkegiatan di bidang musik, khususnya musik-musik Jepang. Kali ini 7 pemuda pemudi dari divisi musik UKJ berkumpul dalam sebuah band dan akan menampilkan lagu yang bakal menghibur kalian~</p>\n<p><strong>Dance Performance</strong></p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_3497\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3497\" data-attachment-id=\"3497\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/hotaru-itb-ciayo-comics-datang-lagi-ke-bandung/attachment/body2-22/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/body2-11.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"ODORI UKJ ITB (Facebook.com)\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;ODORI UKJ ITB (Facebook.com)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/body2-11-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/body2-11.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-3497\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/body2-11.jpg\" alt=\"ODORI UKJ ITB (Facebook.com)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/body2-11.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/body2-11-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-3497\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">ODORI UKJ ITB (Facebook.com)</p></div></p>\n<p>Odori UKJ ITB adalah salah satu divisi di UKJ ITB yang mempelajari tarian-tarian Jepang, mulai dari yang tradisional hingga modern. Di HOTARU kali ini Odori UKJ ITB akan menampilkan beberapa tarian loh~</p>\n<p><strong>Berbagai Komunitas</strong></p>\n<p><strong> </strong></p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_3503\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3503\" data-attachment-id=\"3503\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/hotaru-itb-ciayo-comics-datang-lagi-ke-bandung/attachment/body3-19/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/body3-9.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Kameko.bdg\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Kameko.bdg  (Facebook.com)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/body3-9-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/body3-9.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-3503\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/body3-9.jpg\" alt=\"Kameko.bdg (Facebook.com)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/body3-9.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/body3-9-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-3503\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Kameko.bdg (Facebook.com)</p></div></p>\n<p><strong> </strong></p>\n<p>Kameko.bdg adalah komunitas fotografi cosplay yang bertujuan mengabadikan hasil karya para cosplayer di Indonesia, khususnya di Bandung.</p>\n<p><strong>Merchandise</strong></p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_3512\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3512\" data-attachment-id=\"3512\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/hotaru-itb-ciayo-comics-datang-lagi-ke-bandung/attachment/body7-15/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/body7-5.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Merchandise di HOTARU 6 (Facebook.com)\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Merchandise di HOTARU 6 (Facebook.com)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/body7-5-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/body7-5.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-3512\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/body7-5.jpg\" alt=\"Merchandise di HOTARU 6 (Facebook.com)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/body7-5.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/body7-5-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-3512\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Merchandise di HOTARU 6 (Facebook.com)</p></div></p>\n<p>Di HOTARU kamu juga bisa menemukan berbagai macam merchandise. Salah satunya adalah pin bergambar anime imut!</p>\n<p><strong>Dan masih banyak acara lainnya!</strong></p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_3509\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3509\" data-attachment-id=\"3509\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/hotaru-itb-ciayo-comics-datang-lagi-ke-bandung/attachment/body6-18/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/body6-7.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"CIAYO Comics di HOTARU 6 (Facebook.com)\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;CIAYO Comics di HOTARU 6 (Facebook.com)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/body6-7-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/body6-7.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-3509\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/body6-7.jpg\" alt=\"CIAYO Comics di HOTARU 6 (Facebook.com)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/body6-7.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/body6-7-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-3509\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">CIAYO Comics di HOTARU 6 (Facebook.com)</p></div></p>\n<p>Oh iya! CIAYO Comics juga bakal ikutan meramaikan acara HOTARU 6 ini. Di event ini, CIAYO Comics Situs Komik Online Gratis bakal bagi-bagi banyak hadiah buat pembaca setia CIAYO Comics. Kamu juga bisa tanya-tanya langsung tentang komik CIAYO favoritmu di <em>booth</em> kita. Nantikan juga komik keren  petualangan Mayumi, Megumi dan Shirazune di HOTARU 6 yang bakal tayang di CIAYO Comics ya!</p>\n<p>Jadi, tunggu apalagi? Yuk dateng ke HOTARU 6 pada hari Minggu, 21 Mei 2017 di Lapangan CC Barat dan CC Timur ITB. Acaranya dimulai pukul 10.00 WIB – selesai, dan tiket masuknya GRATIS!</p>\n<p>Untuk info lebih lanjut, langsung kunjungi halaman Facebooknya di <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hotaruitb/\">www.facebook.com/hotaruitb</a></p>\n"}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"id":"48b41bd5-0cdd-568e-89b5-c00a78948db3"}}}